# ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI coding assistants & LLM-generated / memory files
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Claude Code (Anthropic)
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md
CLAUDE_MEM.md          # sometimes seen in plugins
.claude/
.claudeignore          # proposed / emerging in some discussions

# Cursor.sh
.cursorrules
.cursor/
.cursor/rules/
.cursorignore
.cursor.md             # rare, but sometimes used

# Windsurf
.windsurfrules
.windsurf/
.windsurf/rules/

# Other common AI agent memory / rules files
AGENTS.md
.copilot-instructions.md
.github/copilot-instructions.md
JULES.md               # Google / Jules related
.claude/rules/         # hierarchical rules dir
.claude/rules/**/*.md

# Temporary / generated AI files (plugins, auto-memory, experiments)
**/CLAUDE.md           # catch them anywhere (very common with buggy plugins)
**/*.ai.md
**/*.llm.md
**/*.generated.md
.ai/
.llm/
.agent-memory/
.auto-memory/

# General "don't commit AI junk" catch-all (optional, can be noisy)
*AI-README*.md
*ai-generated*
*claude-snapshot*
